Highly available:
  6 copies of your data across 3AZ

Shared Storage Volume::::Replication+Self Healing+Auto Expanding from 10G to 64TB

One Aurora instance takes writes(master).

Automated failover
  15 read replicas(autoscaling enabled as well)
  Cross Region Replication
  
Writer Endpoint- Pointing to the master

READER ENDPOINT: connection load balancing: connects automatically with all the read replicas.
Load balancing happens at the connection level; not the statement level.

